MNN (Mobile Neural Network)
===========================

Project: MNN
Upstream: https://github.com/alibaba/MNN
Version used by LanXin Android: 3.6.0
Packaging:
  - Prebuilt Android shared libraries from official release zip
    mnn_3.6.0_android_armv7_armv8_cpu_opencl_vulkan.zip
    (extracted arm64-v8a/*.so into app/src/main/jniLibs at build time; not committed)
  - Public headers under third_party/mnn/include (MNN + llm engine headers)
  - Thin JNI wrapper libmnn_lanxin.so built from app/src/main/cpp/

License: Apache License 2.0
Full text: https://github.com/alibaba/MNN/blob/master/LICENSE

Copyright: Alibaba Group Holding Limited and MNN contributors.

Notes for LanXin:
- Runtime native libraries are downloaded at Gradle build time (downloadMnnNative).
- LLM model weights (*.mnn / *.mnn.weight / tokenizer) are NOT redistributed in this
  repository; users place them under LanXin/models/local-llm/ (see docs/local-inference.md
  and docs/debug-assets.md).
- Official demo apps/Android/MnnLlmChat is reference only; LanXin uses a minimal JNI
  surface (load / generate / unload) over MNN::Transformer::Llm.
